verbose_text: In a previous study, we combined R 1 and R 2 * to evaluate the changes in tumor pO 2 induced by a hyperoxic gas breathing challenge.14 The aim of the current study was to further validate the combined endogenous MRI contrast parameters R 1 (including R 1G, R 1W and R 1L) and R 2 * to assess the change in tumor oxygenation.
